&gt; *Web developers*: Positive (
&gt; &lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c/webappsec-csp/pull/693#issuecomment-2501689386"&gt;https://github.com/w3c/webappsec-csp/pull/693#issuecomment-2501689386&lt;/a&gt;)
&gt; Shopify as well as Google Security are interested in this.
