&lt;span class="date"&gt;&lt;a href="/search?l=blink-dev@chromium.org&amp;q=date:20241218" rel="nofollow"&gt;Wed, 18 Dec 2024 08:40:11 -0800&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
