&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; None. The last blocking issue
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; &lt;&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/10520"&gt;https://github.com/w3c/csswg-drafts/issues/10520&lt;/a&gt;&gt; was closed this
&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; week.
